txt.en: 'I care not where the spiders went, so long as they are gone!'
'Shh... listen. That is the forest breathing new life.'
'Mirkwood no longer. Greenleaves shall our wood be named.'
'If the King closes the roads, he does so with good reason.'
'Starlight, moonlight, that is the time for dance and song!'
'We have not always dwelled this far north. Perhaps we will not always!'
